{
  "stem": "21786.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You marched on this brick kind of tunnel between the two chimneys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were selecting people who is capable to go work, and who isn't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "With the males, it went relatively smoothly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And with the females, it was a living tragedy, for they were spitting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "First of all, they were naked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The women were naked, and they were making fun of them, and screaming at them, and spitting at them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Anyhow, we were divided into people who were capable of work, and who were not.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they made a transport of thousands men, young men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was in that group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were supposed, on the 1st of July, 1944, to leave the camp to be transferred somewhere to a different camp for work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So we gathered, and under command of the SS men, about 50 SS men with some machine guns.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they marched out of the gate-- which was wide open for us, five abreast.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they took us to the one road which went through the camp number two, and camp number three, which was built.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "On the right side were two crematoria, hidden in these birches.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "On the left side, there was something called sauna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The sauna was actually where-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] showers with all kinds of facilities and similar.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there was also the distribution of clothing, of prisoner clothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And as we marched, they let us halt at the point where there was the crossover between the crematoria and between the sauna.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We knew already that the special commando was not called to do duty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We knew that there is a train, empty train, with a normal, I mean, personal wagon standing there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we didn't know whether this is all a game or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
